channel_info.description:
I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.

transcription: {"text": "High school friends weren't really that good with girls, so I could like backwards rationalize why I wasn't having success. I was like, well, no one's having success. But when I got to college, I had like a new group of friends and they were all like pretty good and they were all getting laid. So I was like, fuck, you know, I'm like the only virgin in my group. I actually started getting into online, like getting laid online through Craigslist. There was, I was reading like a community post or like a forum post where one guy was talking about how he made a post under Craigslist for like, you know, like a very Fifty Shades of Grey style like ad and he banged a girl from that. And I was like, well, this isn't even written that well, I could write this better. So I wrote a much better, you know, version of an ad and it was just kind of like an experiment. I didn't actually think it was gonna work. I was just like, in fact, I didn't even check my email for like two hours and I look at my email and I have like, you know, a lot of spam obviously, but there's also one chick who was like, hey, I love your ad, I'm free tonight, let's hang out. And then I wound up meeting up with her and hooking up with her and I was like, holy shit, this is way easier than cold approach.
